My full studio is now empty. Let the road trip begin.  T R A C E S  Finding the flow between Fragility and Fortitude. @nuartgallery #santafe #faunaflorafigure 

In my latest body of work, Traces, I’m focused on finding the flow state between fragility and fortitude. Each painting starts with web-like drips and intricate patterns that gracefully lay the groundwork for what lies ahead. The hesitant traces underpin the more confident, deliberate passages of earthy colors and complex organic shapes that layer up to the finished painting. The results continue to reflect my deep connection to nature, yet now are more revealing. The fluidity between my own vulnerable self and the tenacity it takes to flourish seems more apparent than ever. Art reflecting life reflecting art...and so it goes.
